FT  10 MAR 92 / World News in Brief: English crime rise
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The number of recorded crimes in England and Wales rose 16 per cent to 5.3m
last year, with crime up in all police force areas. Violent crime rose 6 per
cent last year, and car crimes accounted for nearly a third of the overall
increase of 730,000 offences.
